var getTitleDayView = exports.getTitleDayView = function getTitleDayView(moment) {
  return function (month, year) {
    return moment().month(month).year(year).format('MMMM YYYY');
  };
};
 
var getTitleMonthView = exports.getTitleMonthView = function getTitleMonthView(moment) {
  return function (year) {
    return moment().year(year).format('YYYY');
  };
};
 
var getTitleYearView = exports.getTitleYearView = function getTitleYearView(moment) {
  return function (startYear, endYear) {
    return moment().year(startYear).format('YYYY') + '-' + moment().year(endYear).format('YYYY');
  };
};
 
var getYearRange = exports.getYearRange = function getYearRange(moment) {
  return function (year) {
    var selectedYear = moment().year(year);
    var start = selectedYear.clone().subtract(7, 'years');
    var end = selectedYear.clone().add(4, 'years');
    return { start: start, end: end };
  };
};
 
var getDays = exports.getDays = function getDays(moment) {
  return function (month, year) {
    var selectedMonth = moment().year(year).month(month);
    var start = selectedMonth.clone().date(1).startOf('week');
    var end = selectedMonth.clone().endOf('month').endOf('week');
    return moment.range(start, end).toArray('days');
  };
};
 
var getMonths = exports.getMonths = function getMonths(moment) {
  return function (year) {
    var selectedYear = moment().year(year);
    var start = selectedYear.clone().startOf('year');
    var end = selectedYear.clone().endOf('year');
    return moment.range(start, end).toArray('months');
  };
};
 
var getYears = exports.getYears = function getYears(moment) {
  return function (year) {
    var getYearRangeMoment = getYearRange(moment);
 
    var _getYearRangeMoment = getYearRangeMoment(year);
 
    var start = _getYearRangeMoment.start;
    var end = _getYearRangeMoment.end;
 
    return moment.range(start, end).toArray('years');
  };
};
